short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Xoom Redirector transparently redirects any meeting links to use Zoom's browser based web client.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Note: Prior to March 2022 this extension was called "Zoom Redirector". Zoom issued a trademark violation against this extension and had Google take it down, so it is now called "Xoom Redirector".
